00:47:22,553 --> 00:47:24,443
And when I was ten-years-old...

798
00:47:25,678 --> 00:47:26,678
He died.

799
00:47:29,802 --> 00:47:31,485
He was a drunk who got...

800
00:47:32,550 --> 00:47:34,058
